Class CommandTreeBase

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.minecraft.command.CommandBase
      • net.minecraftforge.server.command.CommandTreeBase
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<ICommand>, ICommand
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CommandTreeHelp, ForgeCommand

    public abstract class CommandTreeBase
extends CommandBase
    Base class for commands that has subcommands.

    E.g. /team settings set [value] settings is subcommand of team and set is subcommand of settings
